    "sousNom": "Red-Elves",
    "race": "Elven",
    "description": "This people, known by few and called as such as ruby elves or red elves, have skin as red and radiant as rubies. Red elves have ardent hearts and live life with passion. Their society is reclusive, little known, and quite secretive; for some, they are merely legends, while others see them as outcasts who chose seclusion over facing the consequences of their ancestors' actions.\n\nUrganian Elves are reclusive, mystical, and fierce. They are known for their deep connection to magic and meditation, often adopting an austere, disciplined lifestyle that emphasizes self-control and focus. Unlike other elves, Urganians exhibit a strict, almost authoritarian attitude. Though rare, they are known for their strategic prowess in both magical and tactical domains. They are also skilled in persuasion and subtlety, often using their knowledge and experience to influence others indirectly.",
